insertion_sort(List, Sorted) :- 
    insertion_sort(List, [], Sorted).

insertion_sort([], Acc, Acc).
insertion_sort([H|T], Acc, Sorted) :-
    insert(H, Acc, NewAcc),
    insertion_sort(T, NewAcc, Sorted).

insert(X, [], [X]).
insert(X, [Y|Ys], [X,Y|Ys]) :-
    X =< Y.
insert(X, [Y|Ys], [Y|Zs]) :-
    X > Y,
    insert(X, Ys, Zs).
 
query(insertion_sort([3,1,2,5,7,12],X)).
